  "where_it_fits": "Accessible from the Institution > Clients flow and via the Clients shortcut in the left sidebar, the Loan Account module is reached when initiating a new loan from a Client Detail page or when opening an existing loan from client listings; it sits in the transaction lifecycle between loan product configuration (Loan Products) and accounting/repayment management (Transactions, Accounting).",
  "assumed_state_on_entry": "User is authenticated with loan-management permissions and is either viewing a specific Client's Detail page (to start a new application) or selecting an existing Loan Account for inspection or action."
